== Welcome to HAML Snippets for GEdit

This is my little addition to GEdit text editor.

I was looking for HAML snippets for GEdit but I couldn't find any so I created one myself.
There aren't many of them yet but I am stiil working on it. I will probbably finish it very soon.
Anyway there are all mostly needed by me :)

I hope it will be usefull for anyone.


== Installation guide


Automatic
Just run install.sh script.

Manual
Just put the downloaded haml.xml file in ~/.gnome2/gedit/snippets directory and restart GEdit.
